Intelligent Transport Systems (ITS) Market FAQs
1. What is Intelligent Transport Systems (ITS)?
Intelligent Transport Systems (ITS) refer to advanced technological solutions applied to transportation and traffic management for improved efficiency, safety, and sustainability.

2. What are the key components of ITS?
The key components of ITS include advanced traffic management systems, electronic toll collection systems, vehicle-to-infrastructure communication, and smart transportation infrastructure.

